snippet.textDisplay:
Ok. Okay. So, for numerous reasons this is my very favorite video EVERRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRR. My kitty Brak passed away in 2018 and it was the worst thing ever. He was almost seventeen and I got him when he was a wee tiny behbeh kitteh and therefore he was my son. I considered making things out of cat hair and found a place online you can ship the cat hair (that you've collected) to, and they wash/sanitize/dry it for you, then card it and send it back in a nice skein, the way you'd get wool or whatever. I didn't get a chance to do that before he passed, but I have a small box with his fluff in it that sits near his ashes, and every so often when the crying hits me again, I can at least touch that a bit and feel better.

So, while yes, this is a weird thing to do - kinda - I absolutely love that you're making a video about it, because you're my favorite Youtuber ever of all time, and Opie looks/acts just like Brak (except Brak was all white with blue eyes). Thank you for doing this, even though I'm weepy now.
snippet.textOriginal:
Ok.  Okay.  So, for numerous reasons this is my very favorite video EVERRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRRR.  My kitty Brak passed away in 2018 and it was the worst thing ever.  He was almost seventeen and I got him when he was a wee tiny behbeh kitteh and therefore he was my son.  I considered making things out of cat hair and found a place online you can ship the cat hair (that you've collected) to, and they wash/sanitize/dry it for you, then card it and send it back in a nice skein, the way you'd get wool or whatever.  I didn't get a chance to do that before he passed, but I have a small box with his fluff in it that sits near his ashes, and every so often when the crying hits me again, I can at least touch that a bit and feel better.  

So, while yes, this is a weird thing to do - kinda - I absolutely love that you're making a video about it, because you're my favorite Youtuber ever of all time, and Opie looks/acts just like Brak (except Brak was all white with blue eyes).  Thank you for doing this, even though I'm weepy now.
